high_descs: Walk around the kitchen island to the counter left of the stove
Pick up the right most spoon from the counter
Turn left and walk to the fridge
Put the spoon into the orange mug inside the fridge
Pick up the mug from the fridge
Turn left and walk over to the sink
Put the mug down in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with spoon into the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right side of the fridge.
Pick up the spoon furthest to the right.
Turn left and face the fridge.
Put the spoon in the orange cup in the fridge.
Pick up the orange cup in the fridge.
Turn around and walk right to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the spoon on the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the spoon closest to the stove.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Place the spoon inside the right most bowl inside the fridge.
Pick up the bowl with a spoon in it and then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl with a spoon in it inside the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight to the refrigerator, turn right, walk towards the counter to the right of the refrigerator.
Take the completely silver spoon from the counter.
Open the refrigerator on the left.
Put the spoon in the bowl that is in the refrigerator.
Take the bowl with the spoon in it from the refrigerator.
Turn left, walk towards the sink, stop in front of the sink.
Put the bowl with the spoon into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with the spoon in it into the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the door, then make a right at the refrigerator, and go to the small counter top between the stove and refrigerator.
Pick up the spoon by the stove.
Turn to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the spoon in the orange cup, on the shelf above the drawers.
Pick up the orange cup with the spoon inside it.
Turn to your left and walk to the sink.
Place the orange cup with the spoon inside, in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup, containing a spoon in the sink.

pick up the spoon that is on the counter
take two steps to the left to face fridge
open fridge, put spoon in cup that is on shelf in fridge
take cup with spoon out of fridge
turn around, take two steps, turn right, walk forward, turn left after island, turn right to go to sink
put spoon with cup in the sink
